name: Re-Up 2.0 Headphone Tee (Preorder)
description:
Here's your chance to get our deadstock Re-Up 2.0 T-Shirt that even comes with a fresh design that makes it look like you have over -ear headphones around your neck! cop the pre-order and don't forget that were donating $1 from each T-Shirt purchased to Christ House Homeless Shelter in Alexandria, VA 

Pre-Orders go out on the re-launch of The-Re-Up.com which is JUNE 8th!
